snippet: An Israeli airstrike killed three Palestinian militants in the Gaza Strip late Wednesday and seriously wounded a fourth, according to Palestinian and Israeli officials.
abstract: Palestinian and Israeli officials report that an Israeli airstrike killed three Palestinian militants in the Gaza Strip and seriously wounded a fourth; Israel says the militants had been preparing to launch a rocket to attack Israel.
lead_paragraph: An Israeli airstrike killed three Palestinian militants in the Gaza Strip late Wednesday and seriously wounded a fourth, according to Palestinian and Israeli officials.
